### Create Admin User (Admin Only)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/create-admin/
Authorization: Bearer {admin_access_token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin.staff@example.com",
  "password": "AdminPass123!",
  "number_type": "Service Number BA/BSS",
  "number": "BA/BSS-ADMIN-001",
  "phone": "+880-2222222222",
  "whatsapp_number": "+880-2222222222"
}

# NOTE: This endpoint requires admin/staff authentication
# Steps to use:
# 1. Get admin access token by logging in with existing admin account
# 2. Replace {admin_access_token} with the actual access_key from login
# 3. The new admin user will be created with:
#    - is_active = True (immediately active)
#    - is_staff = True (can access admin panel)
#    - is_superuser = False (not a superuser, just staff)

